 soul is in a child, but he does not know who it is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If the child dies, Azazil dies at the same time. The magic of the wizard who imprisoned him in Pandora's box circulates in his blood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The devils are gathering all the children in the villages. Azazil wants to detect the child with his own magic and neutralize this spell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Then, a creature that takes Ares' son to the temple is shot by an archer and the child falls into the middle of a mountain, lonely and helpless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ares seeks the help of a most talented and knowledgeable wizard to find his son and avenge all that has happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">and he goes on this way, his magic ability develops over time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will Ares find his son?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will he save the world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What will happen to other peoples?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is he alone?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2255910/extras/banner_story__1_.png?t=1729341419\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different scenarios for each different nationality with shield and flag selection and customizable at start.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many side quests outside the main story such as fishing, riding horses, helping a villager, digging a field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">87 different melee weapons such as Ax, Sword, Halberd, Bardiche, Bilhook, Dagger, Shield, Heavy Sword, Mace, Messer, Partisan, Angled Axe, Sax, Spear, Voulge, Warhammer and Zweihander</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than 